00:08:25.920 --> 00:08:33.640
take that much time. So I stopped having that much time to play games. But yeah, eventually

00:08:33.640 --> 00:08:38.799
I was all surpassed and I'm just a drop in the ocean at this point. If you look at the

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:42.520
