a big one where it was like reading a CSV in Pandas, as it turned out, was like a big

00:10:49.640 --> 00:10:53.239
kind of like getting that fast was its own.

00:10:53.239 --> 00:11:04.599
Yeah, it's a huge bottleneck. And this is going back to like 2011. I think we had built,

00:11:04.599 --> 00:11:09.320
like I had built like a fairly primitive CSV parser reader for Pandas that was written

